 Watch'' (2014\u20132015)\n{{Div col end}}\n\n=== Variety shows ===\n*''[[Wild 'n Out|Nick Cannon Presents: Wild 'n Out]]'' (2005\u201319, moved to [[VH1]])\n*''[[Safeword_(game_show)#International_adaptations|SafeWord]]'' (2017-2018)\n\n=== Scripted shows ===\n==== Drama ====\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n*''[[$5 Cover]]'' (2009)\n*''[[Catwalk (Canadian TV series)|Catwalk]]'' (1992\u20131994)\n*''[[Dead at 21]]'' (1994)\n*''[[Eye Candy (TV series)|Eye Candy]]'' (2015)\n*''[[Finding Carter]]'' (2014\u201315)\n*''[[Kaya (TV series)|Kaya]]'' (2007)\n*''[[Live Through This (TV series)|Live Through This]]'' (2000)\n*''[[Scream (TV series)|Scream]]'' (2015\u201316, moved to [[VH1]])\n*''[[Skins (American TV series)|Skins]]'' (2011)\n*''[[Spyder Games]]'' (2001)\n*''[[Sweet/Vicious]]'' (2016)\n*''[[Teen Wolf (2011 TV series)|Teen Wolf]]'' (2011\u201317)\n*''[[The Shannara Chronicles]]'' (2016, moved to [[Paramount_Network#Spike_TV_(2003\u20132018)|Spike TV]])\n*''[[Undressed]]'' (1999\u20132002)\n*''[[Valemont]]'' (2009\u201310)\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==== Comedy ====\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* ''1/2 Hour Comedy Hour'' (1988)\n* ''[[2gether (band)#2gether: The Series|2ge+her]]'' (2000\u201301)\n* ''Acting Out'' (2016)\n* ''[[Al TV]]'' (1984\u201399)\n* ''[[Apartment 2F]]'' (1997)\n* ''[[Austin Stories]]'' (1997\u201398)\n* ''[[Awkward (TV series)|Awkward.]]'' (2011\u201316)\n* ''Blastazoid'' (2006)\n* ''[[Blowin' Up]]'' (2006\u201307)\n* ''[[Buzzkill (TV series)|Buzzkill]]'' (1996)\n* ''[[Comikaze]]'' (1993)\n* ''[[Connected (TV series)|Connected]]'' (2007)\n* ''[[Death Valley (TV series)|Death Valley]]'' (2011)\n* ''[[Doggy Fizzle Televizzle]]'' (2002\u201303)\n* ''[[Faking It (American TV series)|Faking It]]'' (2014\u201316)\n* ''[[Girl Code]]'' (2013\u201315)\n* ''[[Happyland (TV series)|Happyland]]'' (2014)\n* ''[[Human Giant]]'' (2007\u201308)\n* ''[[I Just Want My Pants Back]]'' (2011\u201312)\n* ''[[Inside Amy Schumer]]'' (2015)\n* ''[[Jackass (franchise)|Jackass]]''