on]] channel which was the first television channel dedicated to [[music]], [[music industry]] and [[Music history|history]] in the United States upon its founding in 1981. [[MTV Networks]] has since produced various original television shows, many of which concern genres unrelated to music. This is an incomplete list of MTV shows that have aired.\n\n==Current programming==\n===Music shows===\n*''[[MTV Unplugged]]'' (1989)\n*''[[Total Request Live]]'' (1998\u20132008; 2017)\n*''[[MTV#Post-TRL live shows (2009\u2013present)|MTV First]]'' (2011)\n\n=== Reality shows ===\n*''[[Teen Mom|Teen Mom OG]]'' (2009)\n*''[[Teen Mom 2]]'' (2011)\n*''[[Catfish: The TV Show]]'' (2012)\n*''Amazingness'' (2017)\n*''[[Floribama Shore]]'' (2017)\n*''[[Siesta Key (TV series)|Siesta Key]]'' (2017)\n*''Promposal'' (2017)\n*''[[How Far Is Tattoo Far?]]'' (2018)\n*''[[Jersey Shore: Family Vacation]]'' (2018)\n*''[[Ex on the Beach (American TV series)|Ex on the Beach]]'' (2018)\n*''[[Teen Mom: Young and Pregnant]]'' (2018)\n*''Game of Clones'' (2019)\n*''Tana Turns 21'' (2019)\n*''[[The Hills: New Beginnings]]'' (2019)\n*''[[Ghosted: Love Gone Missing]]'' (2019)\n*''True Life Crime'' (2020)\n*''[[The Busch Family Brewed]]'' (2020)\n\n===Competitive shows===\n*''[[The Challenge (TV series)|The Challenge]]'' (1998)\n*''[[Are You the One?]]'' (2014)\n*''[[The Challenge: Champs vs. Stars]]'' (2017)\n\n===Variety shows===\n*''[[Ridiculousness (TV series)|Ridiculousness]]'' (2011)\n\n==Upcoming programming==\n*''DJ Pauly D & Vinny's Vegas Pool Party'' (2020)<ref>{{cite web|title=MTV Continues Its Hot Streak as the #1 Network in Prime with Greenlight of \"DJ Pauly D & Vinny's Vegas Pool Party\"|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2019/10/01/mtv-continues-its-hot-streak-as-the-number-1-network-in-prime-with-greenlight-of-dj-pauly-d-and-vinnys-vegas-pool-party-601011/20191001mtv01/|work=[[The Futon Critic]]|date=October 1, 2019}}</ref>\n*''[[Making the Band]]'' (Revival) (2020)<ref>{{cite web|tit