imes.com/1993-08-29/news/tv-28918_1_premieres-sept/2 | title=The Kids' Plate : NETWORK, CABLE AND INDEPENDENTS OFFER A FULL COURSE OF LIVE-ACTION AND ANIMATION | publisher=Los Angeles Times | date=29 August 1993 | accessdate=5 February 2016}}</ref> || colspan=\"2\"|1993\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\" | ''[[SpongeBob SquarePants]]'' <ref>{{cite web |title=MTV.com - On-Air - MTV Week at a Glance |url=http://www.mtv.com/onair/schedule/mtv/weekly.jhtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080725175551/http://www.mtv.com/onair/schedule/mtv/weekly.jhtml |archivedate=25 July 2008 |url-status=dead}}</ref> || 2000 || 2016\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\" | ''[[That '70s Show]]'' <ref>{{cite web |title=MTV.com - On-Air - MTV Week at a Glance |url=http://www.mtv.com/onair/schedule/mtv/weekly.jhtml |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110308113015/http://www.mtv.com/onair/schedule/mtv/weekly.jhtml |archivedate=8 March 2011 |url-status=dead}}</ref> || 2010 || 2013\n|-\n| scope=\"row\" style=\"text-align:left;\" | ''[[The Young Ones (TV series)|The Young Ones]]'' || 1987 || 1988\n|}\n\n== Special events ==\n\n=== Seasonal or annual ===\n{{div col|colwidth=30em}}\n* ''All Access Week'' (1999\u20132002)\n* ''[[Camp MTV]]'' (1989)\n* ''Fashionably Loud'' (1997)\n* ''Hottest MCs in the Game'' (2007\u2013present)\n* ''Isle of MTV Malta Special'' (1999\u2013present)\n* ''Motel California'' (1997)\n* ''MTV Tr3s presents: The Wintery Christmas Fiesta'' (2007\u201308)\n* ''MTV's Beach House''\n* ''MTV's Live and Loud'' (1993)\n* ''MTV's New Year's Eve'' (1981\u2013present)\n* ''MTV's Shore Thing'' (2002)\n* ''MTV's Summer Share'' (1998)\n* ''SoCal Summer'' (2000)\n* ''Springer Break'' (1998)\n* ''Summer in the Keys'' (2001)\n* ''Summer on the Run'' (2004)\n* ''Summer on the Strip'' (2005)\n* ''Summer Sizzle'' (2006)\n* ''Spankin' Free Music Week'' (1999\u20132005)\n* ''Spankin' New Music Week'' (2006)\n{{Div col end}}\n\n=== Award shows ===\n{{For